      <title>SNAP benefits set to expire this week. And, Jamaica braces for a Category 5 storm</title>
      <author>Brittney Melton</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/10/28/g-s1-95325/up-first-newsletter-food-assistance-benefits-trump-japan-hurricane-melissa</link>
