      <title>Shutdown to impact federal workers' pay. And, tensions grow between U.S. and Colombia</title>
      <author>Brittney Melton</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/10/21/g-s1-94344/up-first-newsletter-government-shutdown-federal-employees-colombia-louvre</link>
