      <title>Gaza ceasefire deal violated. And, shutdown enters day 20 with no end in sight</title>
      <author>Brittney Melton</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/10/20/g-s1-94232/up-first-newsletter-israel-gaza-government-shutdown-colombia-venezuela-boats</link>
